      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AKINA LAD (8) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Filled a minor placings again last time when third (23.08) at Warragul making it three placings in a row. Has a good record here at this journey. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Well placed and gets his chance. DOCTOR MINTY (7) started big odds but ran one of the quickest times of the card with a neck win (24.58) at this track latest. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Can make it two on the bounce. DR. KATARINA (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at Traralgon following on from a third place finish (24.83) at this track the start prior. Solid record here at the distance winning six races. The form out of her last race has been franked. Better than last start and can bounce back. VALENCIA JIM (3) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
